node.text: Fathers, sometimes our children just need that one moment of our support to guide them in the right direction or launch their dreams. Here's a story of how my father did that for me.

node.title: My father was my biggest supporter.

node.text:
Not being successful is hard too. Let me tell you the difference between the two. 

Difficulties are a part of your journey to success but there is joy in the journey to success. #motivation #steveharvey

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Steve Harvey on July 20, 2021 tagging @daninirvana, @djbrandigarcia, @thachman, @itsaaronbernard, and @deniseconsulting. May be an image of 4 people and text that says 'YOU GOT IT! OVERCOMING SELF-DOUBT ON YOUR JOURNEY TO PURPOSE AMBASSADOR MEET AND GREET JULY 20 @ 7PM EST @DANINIRVANA PURPOSE PARTNER @DJBRANDIGARCIA LIFESTYLE INFLUENCER @DENISECONSULTING WEALTH BUILDER SPEAKER VAULT 365 @ITSAARONBERNARD MENTAL HEALTH ADVOCATE @THACHMAN BRAND STRATEGIST Vault Empowers POWERED POWERED'.

node.text: TONIGHT IS THE NIGHT! @VaultEmpowers is hosting the first Vault 365 Ambassador Meet and Greet for all Vault 365 members at 7PM EST / 4PM PST. Our five ambassadors will be sharing tips in their fields including finance, brand development, and following your passion, just to name a few. There's still time to register - Link in bio to become a member today to join this event.
